  "fun_fact": "We are living in an era of <a href=\"https://news.un.org/en/story/2026/01/1166800\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">global water bankruptcy</a> — demand far outstrips supply. India, home to 18% of the world's population but just 4% of its freshwater, is one of the most water-stressed nations on Earth. Do you know how much water an avg person needs every day? <a href=\"https://sunnyclimatestormyclimate.substack.com/p/wading-through-ignorance-why-we-need?utm_source=publication-search\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find out!</a>",
